question: how high is the share of people living in proximity of a busstop in Bonstetten?
sql:
select iv.value from indicator_values2 iv
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where i.name like 'Access by bus [% of inhabitants]' and s.name like 'Bonstetten'

question: How many municipalities currently have a share of people living in proximity of a busstop higher than 75.6?
sql:
select count(*) from
indicator_values2 iv
inner join (select indicator_id, value, MAX(year) 
            from indicator_values2) iv2 on iv2.indicator_id = iv.indicator_id
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where iv.VALUE > 75.6 and s.type_id = 1 and i.name like 'Access by bus [% of inhabitants]'
